{"tid":2316014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第4支神秘金屬柱疑現身英國懷特島","createTime":"2020-12-07T14:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T06:31:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":142,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"547a399e84827944b9ae4867e04756d3a7aead09","tid":2316014,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"美國猶他州沙漠前陣子突然出現約3公尺高的神秘金屬柱狀物，沒想到緊接著美國加州、羅馬尼亞也接連出現。昨（6日）早上再次在英國懷特島上發現第4根金屬柱狀物。<br />\n<br />\n據《skynews》報導，島上的29歲居民鄧福德（Tom Dunford）一早7時30分和未婚妻、妹妹一起在康普頓海灘上遛狗，意外發現了這個金屬柱狀物。<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德說：「我最近有關注金屬柱狀物的新聞，所以一看到就馬上認出來了。」這次的金屬柱狀物與過去相似，高約3公尺。鄧福德描述，當時他從台階上走下來，一眼看到右前方約90公尺處，金屬柱狀物正反射著陽光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3374287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3374287&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7BmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=21e7b6ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3374287&h=ce379d0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3374287</a>"},{"pid":"1d79e685a3abfc1386a0468f20ce787764c6f5ec","tid":2316014,"uid":20170,"like":186,"dislike":6,"score":180,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:18:21.000Z","msg":"跟風當有趣"},{"pid":"058fe3c40a1111e780d09ccad25721c9ffe1cc6c","tid":2316014,"uid":184679,"like":115,"dislike":5,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQC0EZvxXvP9db6YcwcbjR4TpD2dpK0BCdTMA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQC0EZvxXvP9db6YcwcbjR4TpD2dpK0BCdTMA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=b6e5089c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71a4dc492cbdbf2845a02b3cd7195be35f54d2d3","tid":2316014,"uid":50327,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"煉成陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"h